🎯 ROUND 3: PRODUCT COMPANY STYLE QUESTIONS 🔥
🧠 Q7: Why threads are preferred over processes?
✅ Answer (Impressive)

Threads are preferred because they are lightweight, share memory, have faster context switching, and allow efficient communication.

🧠 Q8: Why cache improves performance?
✅ Answer

Cache reduces memory access time by storing frequently used data close to CPU, based on locality of reference.

🧠 Q9: Why deadlock is difficult to handle?
✅ Answer

Because it involves multiple processes waiting cyclically, making it complex to detect and recover without affecting system stability.

